description: Try our easy to follow Homemade Baked Beans recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Breakfast,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Father's Day,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Homemade Baked Beans Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a frying pan over medium heat. Add onion, bacon and chilli flakes. Cook for 5 minutes or until bacon is golden.

Add tomatoes, maple syrup, vinegar, molasses and mustard. Stir to combine and bring to the boil. Simmer for 5 minutes or until lightly thickened. Add beans and cook for 15 minutes or until softened. Season before serving.
